# ğŸ“Š Day 16 â€” Sentiment Analysis using LSTM

This project explores **Natural Language Processing (NLP)** using a **Long Short-Term Memory (LSTM)** neural network to perform sentiment analysis on the **IMDB Movie Review Dataset**.  
It classifies reviews as **Positive** or **Negative**, demonstrating how deep learning models can process sequential data for text understanding.

---

## ğŸš€ Overview
- Preprocessed IMDB reviews into padded integer sequences  
- Built an **LSTM model** with an Embedding layer for word vectorization  
- Trained and validated using binary cross-entropy loss  
- Visualized performance via loss, accuracy, and confusion matrix plots  

